{"tid":786480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撚樣優品360°老闆：阿信屋10億樓下我有興趣","createTime":"2018-08-20T03:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:18:43.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b563a1577cf31d0bc2d299b94eaac9c2264af041","tid":786480,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180820&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58584596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180820%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58584596&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=06e6a2fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180820%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58584596&h=4564c098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180820&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58584596</a><br />\n<br />\n【林偉駿病逝】優品360&deg;老闆：阿信屋10億樓下我有興趣<br />\n<br />\n對於759阿信屋創辦人突然離世，作為業務競爭對手的優品360&deg;老闆林子峰向本報表示擔心，因為怕759阿信屋會賣俾一個強者。他不諱言對759阿信屋（即CEC國際（759））有興趣，殼連公司市值約6億元，如果10億元以下都會有興趣，以免被強者崛起打倒自己。<br />\n<br />\n林子峰表示，佢（林偉駿）都唔識做生意，亂咁開舖，開成200幾間。舉例用3萬元租1間舖，租夠5間，先賺150萬元生意，租金佔收入10%。我都係租金佔收入10%，但我15萬元租1間舖做150萬元生意。另外人手及物流控制亦非理想做法。"},{"pid":"9424bf33e68cb5c1e3b01ff00d38ea9015c74cc3","tid":786480,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"支那人就係咁，宇宙毒瘤"},{"pid":"7e9a12113b4a2918294ff2735ff59fc8fc2f772e","tid":786480,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbca50b8477bf7a5ddd5284f00c3f4573b0e6082","tid":786480,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/13335803_10153424367426307_4432384709551300258_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F13335803_10153424367426307_4432384709551300258_n.jpg&h=d7c88e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱烈歡迎！晉江市劉文儒市長，率團蒞臨香港將軍澳翠林新城指導<br />\n<br />\n據知商場買家林子峰是福建人，該次到訪的正是福建省下轄晉江市的市長。"},{"pid":"2dfae47ac20761d8c34bfdb7c249e92e9bc81bd9","tid":786480,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你話林老闆唔識做生意!?<br />\n你業績好似仲差過759喎<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXbNFzEihYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPXbNFzEihYg&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8962143e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXbNFzEihYg</a>"},{"pid":"bf2ac8b997ae8b8b3d3b9c136b66792fc5fb356c","tid":786480,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdad52e37763222d96c8fba65f35aca0762b341","tid":786480,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"up"}]}